# attestation-verify is pure crypto — it needs no network and no secrets.
# This file exists only so the template is self-describing and consistent
# with the other starters; the demo runs with zero configuration.
#
# (Optional) override the demo signing key used to produce the sample
# signed envelope. Any 64-char hex key works; the default is a well-known
# test key and MUST NOT be used for anything real.
# DEMO_PRIVATE_KEY=0x59c6995e998f97a5a0044966f0945389dc9e86dae88c7a8412f4603b6b78690d
